as the investigation of the impact of system\nparameters such as HARQ protocol type, blocklength and number of antennas on\nthe performance of low-latency local HARQ decisions in BBU Hoteling and C-RAN\narchitectures.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 26 Aug 2015 16:56:04 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 28 Aug 2015 16:38:01 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 15 Dec 2015 19:44:43 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Fri, 26 Aug 2016 17:24:42 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Mon, 5 Sep 2016 20:18:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-09-07"}
