 model. On the other hand, the kink instability\nmay destabilize the twisted tornado, and consequently prominence tornadoes can\nbe used as precursors for CMEs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 27 Aug 2015 10:04:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-09-16"}
